      "artifacts": {
        "changelog_entry": "[#364] Sprint D SRS foundation chunk impl - replaces the T-SRS-001 SRSImage skeleton with a concrete Image subclass that requires lambda/y/x, adds a frozen SRSImage.Meta model with the nine locked SRS metadata fields, validates wavenumbers_cm1 length against the lambda axis when shape is known, re-exports SRSImage from the package root, and enables get_types() to return [SRSImage]. The skipped SRS type stubs are replaced with concrete constructor / metadata / registry tests, and tests/plugins/test_phase11_skeleton.py gains test_srs_types_impl_smoke() so the workflow gate sees a top-level SRS implementation signal. (@claude, 2026-04-08, branch: feat/issue-364/T-SRS-001-srsimage-type, session: 20260408-005855-phase-11-srs-foundation-t-srs-001-srsima)"
